  <brief_title>The Effects of Exenatide After Gastric Restriction</brief_title>
  <acronym>AGREE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study of the Effects of BYETTA® (Exenatide) on Weight Loss in Morbidly Obese Non Diabetic Patients Following Adjustable Gastric Banding</official_title>
