  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to describe change in body weight in non-diabetic morbidly obese
      patients after laparoscopic adjustable gastric banding (LAGB) with twice daily exenatide or
      placebo injections.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
